{
  "stem": "22892.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was run by a German-- occupied-- I mean, and there were Jews working on the farmland and whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got there-- I think it was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the reason I remember that day, because there's some Jewish women preparing for the Sabbath-- Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, like busybodies looking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, God, these people are crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you know, I know they're going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then again, but here I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At least I felt among Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Felt-- So I don't know how, but somehow they-- some people asked me to stay there with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- Where was the farm?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Do you know the name of the town?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farm-- it wasn't actually-- it was the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not that many miles I, I-- it just-- I forgot the name of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't=- was just a unique place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just-- really, I mean, if I look at it different, it was just a beautiful area on top of a hill.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a lot of buildings, and there was a row of houses where probably the workers used to live there years ago when they worked the farm.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was like barracks in a way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were, you know, in one room, it was like about eight people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and right after that, that weekend, the Sabbath and just a couple days after that, the woman where I stayed with worked for the German, for that lieutenant who was running the, the-- this farm.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know whether she was the cook or cleaning, but she came in one night and she said that he told her that they're going to kill the Jews in that place.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
